            "content_html": "<a href=\"https://textexpander.com/maximizing-productivity/textexpander-end-of-year-summary-email-a-look-at-your-stats\"><img width=\"600\" height=\"300\" src=\"https://textexpander.com/wp-content/uploads/te-feature-TextExpander-End-of-Year-Summary-Email-600x300.png\" alt=\"TextExpander End of Year Summary Email: A Look At Your Stats\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin: 0 20px 20px 0;max-width:560px;max-width:100%;\" /></a>\n<p>One of the annual highlights at TextExpander is reading your responses to your end of year summary emails. For TextExpander newbies, each year we send out a summary email containing the stats on how much time you\u2019ve saved by using TextExpander. Data from the number and size of the snippets you\u2019ve expanded is used to calculate roughly how many hours, and often days, you\u2019ve saved. There\u2019s more information on\u00a0<a href=\"https://textexpander.com/blog/how-textexpander-calculates-your-time-savings\">how TextExpander works out your time savings here</a>, if you\u2019re curious!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Our end of year summary is easily one of our favorite emails to send out to our community and we love your feedback. Today, we wanted to share with you not only the time that TextExpander users have saved but a look at how they\u2019ve put that time to use. Here\u2019s how much time the TextExpander community is saving!</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"h-so-how-much-time-did-you-save\"><a></a>So How Much Time Did You Save?</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Last year, members of our community clocked up not just hours, but days saved of laborious typing time. For some, it was a couple days freed from typing\u2026</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed is-type-rich is-provider-twitter wp-block-embed-twitter\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">Here's my annual recommendation for <a href=\"https://twitter.com/TextExpander?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@TextExpander</a>, a text auto-replacement program that I've bought and appreciated for many years.<br><br>If you have messages, code, and snippets that you type repeatedly, a program like this is extremely helpful. <a href=\"https://t.co/KvKeHkTL0V\">pic.twitter.com/KvKeHkTL0V</a></p>\u2014 W. Eric Martin (@BoardgameNews) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/BoardgameNews/status/1484211230902558726?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">January 20, 2022</a></blockquote><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n</div></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed is-type-rich is-provider-twitter wp-block-embed-twitter\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">True fact: <a href=\"https://twitter.com/TextExpander?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@TextExpander</a> has an internal log that tells me I save 4 days of typing time in 2021\u2014and 34 days since I started using it over a decade ago. It's the one Mac utility I swear by. <a href=\"https://t.co/6TdiawpLHt\">https://t.co/6TdiawpLHt</a></p>\u2014 Drummond Reed (@drummondreed) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/drummondreed/status/1484234503530762242?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">January 20, 2022</a></blockquote><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n</div></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed is-type-rich is-provider-twitter wp-block-embed-twitter\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">Efficiency win \ud83d\udcaa I saved 5 days last year with <a href=\"https://twitter.com/TextExpander?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@TextExpander</a>, and 21 days since I started 4 years ago! \ud83e\udd29 <a href=\"https://t.co/fi47bDZx51\">https://t.co/fi47bDZx51</a></p>\u2014 Laura Jolly (@LauraEJolly) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/LauraEJolly/status/1484246508828610561?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">January 20, 2022</a></blockquote><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n</div></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"560\" src=\"https://textexpander.com/wp-content/uploads/te-body-TextExpander-End-of-Year-Summary-Email-3-560x400.png\" alt=\"TextExpander LinkedIn Update\" class=\"wp-image-39169\" style=\"display:block;margin:10px auto;max-width:560px;max-width:100%;\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>While others saved over a week thanks to their speedy snippets\u2026</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed is-type-rich is-provider-twitter wp-block-embed-twitter\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">Quick productivity hack with quantified benefits. <br><br>In 2021 I saved 7 days (80 WPM in 8-hour days) using <a href=\"https://twitter.com/TextExpander?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@TextExpander</a> shortcuts instead of typing everything. <br><br>Over the lifetime of use I have now saved 30 days of typing. That is 96,000 keystrokes I haven't had to use<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/phdchat?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#phdchat</a> <a href=\"https://t.co/4OoeuPZf83\">pic.twitter.com/4OoeuPZf83</a></p>\u2014 Prof Mark Hutchinson (@prof_hutchinson) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/prof_hutchinson/status/1484299699209519105?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">January 20, 2022</a></blockquote><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n</div></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed is-type-rich is-provider-twitter wp-block-embed-twitter\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">In 2021, I saved 8 whole days of my life, thanks to <a href=\"https://twitter.com/TextExpander?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@TextExpander</a>.<br><br>Truly a must-have.<br><br>(20% off an annual plan \u2013 <a href=\"https://t.co/0KcqpenDEA\">https://t.co/0KcqpenDEA</a>) <a href=\"https://t.co/ouSozj3SuK\">pic.twitter.com/ouSozj3SuK</a></p>\u2014 Rob Bettis (@robbettis) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/robbettis/status/1484251532283551749?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">January 20, 2022</a></blockquote><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n</div></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed is-type-rich is-provider-twitter wp-block-embed-twitter\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">I saved 10 days last year with <a href=\"https://twitter.com/TextExpander?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@TextExpander</a>! And 36 days since I started. <a href=\"https://t.co/Pz9yrRSwFe\">https://t.co/Pz9yrRSwFe</a></p>\u2014 Don Schaffner \ud83e\udda0 (@bugcounter) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/bugcounter/status/1484219759583539203?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">January 20, 2022</a></blockquote><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n</div></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>And then some users even clocked in with multiple weeks saved in just one year.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed is-type-rich is-provider-twitter wp-block-embed-twitter\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">I saved 33 days last year with <a href=\"https://twitter.com/TextExpander?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@TextExpander</a>! And 91 days since I started. <a href=\"https://t.co/vuTJvIWk4J\">https://t.co/vuTJvIWk4J</a></p>\u2014 \ud83c\udff4\udb40\udc67\udb40\udc62\udb40\udc77\udb40\udc6c\udb40\udc73\udb40\udc7f Stuart \ud83c\udff4\udb40\udc67\udb40\udc62\udb40\udc77\udb40\udc6c\udb40\udc73\udb40\udc7f (@welsh_stu) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/welsh_stu/status/1484236345920925697?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">January 20, 2022</a></blockquote><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n</div></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"560\" src=\"https://textexpander.com/wp-content/uploads/te-body-TextExpander-End-of-Year-Summary-Email-1-560x438.png\" alt=\"TextExpander LinkedIn Update\" class=\"wp-image-39170\" style=\"display:block;margin:10px auto;max-width:560px;max-width:100%;\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"h-how-did-you-spend-that-time\"><a></a>How Did You Spend That Time?</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Some of you even let us know how you put your saved time to good use!</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed is-type-rich is-provider-twitter wp-block-embed-twitter\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">I saved 2 days last year with <a href=\"https://twitter.com/TextExpander?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@TextExpander</a>!  <a href=\"https://t.co/w8Lak1mLBw\">https://t.co/w8Lak1mLBw</a></p>\u2014 Dr Alison Hardy (@hardy_alison) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hardy_alison/status/1484241498266906624?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">January 20, 2022</a></blockquote><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n</div></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed is-type-rich is-provider-twitter wp-block-embed-twitter\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">I\u2019ve been a <a href=\"https://twitter.com/TextExpander?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@TextExpander</a> user for a few years so this figure is cumulative, but WOW.  This equates to 15.5 work-weeks I\u2019ve saved.<br><br>Maybe I should take another <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/epictrip?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#epictrip</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/thesiswhisperer?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@thesiswhisperer</a>?<br><br>I\u2019ve earned it. <br><br>\ud83c\udf66 \ud83c\udf66 \ud83c\udf66 <a href=\"https://t.co/a4TZZRJOcN\">pic.twitter.com/a4TZZRJOcN</a></p>\u2014 Dr. JD (@jasondowns) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/jasondowns/status/1484481996189433857?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">January 21, 2022</a></blockquote><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n</div></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed is-type-rich is-provider-twitter wp-block-embed-twitter\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">.<a href=\"https://twitter.com/TextExpander?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@TextExpander</a> saved me 9 days of typing just last year. That's a lot of ice cream to eat <a href=\"https://twitter.com/jasondowns?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@jasondowns</a>! <a href=\"https://t.co/Z5b1F1ADaP\">pic.twitter.com/Z5b1F1ADaP</a></p>\u2014 Prof Inger Mewburn (@thesiswhisperer) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/thesiswhisperer/status/1484289969464422402?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">January 20, 2022</a></blockquote><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n</div></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>And some of you shared the benefits you experienced, too:</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed is-type-rich is-provider-twitter wp-block-embed-twitter\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">According to <a href=\"https://twitter.com/TextExpander?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@TextExpander</a>, TextExpander has saved me 6 hours in 2021.<br><br>I actually think it's much more than that in terms of \"mental energy saved\"! <a href=\"https://t.co/VzFynUe2Wb\">pic.twitter.com/VzFynUe2Wb</a></p>\u2014 Christoph Janz (@chrija) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/chrija/status/1484435078172315650?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">January 21, 2022</a></blockquote><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n</div></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>And some advice on how to boost your numbers:</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"560\" src=\"https://textexpander.com/wp-content/uploads/te-body-TextExpander-End-of-Year-Summary-Email-2-560x501.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-39171\" style=\"display:block;margin:10px auto;max-width:560px;max-width:100%;\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"h-what-the-textexpander-team-did-with-their-saved-time\"><a></a>What the TextExpander Team Did With Their Saved Time</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>We asked some of the team what they did with all the time they saved using TextExpander this year. Here\u2019s what they said:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>I used that time to write!</li><li>My family bought a house, and I spent every saved hour (and then some!) trying to bring it from 1982 to 2022.</li><li>I used my saved hours to build my spiritual health this past year.</li><li>I spent my time journaling and meditating, both total gamechangers!</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"h-find-out-how-much-time-you-ve-saved\"><a></a>Find Out How Much Time You\u2019ve Saved</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Alongside our emails, you can find out your own TextExpander time savings whenever you\u2019d like to within the app. Simply open the app, select your username, then select \u201cStatistics\u201d to be taken to your stats page.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>How much time did you save this year? Let us know. If you want to boost your stats but don\u2019t know where to start, try these posts:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li><a href=\"https://textexpander.com/blog/textexpander-public-groups-what-you-need-to-know\">TextExpander Public Groups 101</a></li><li><a href=\"https://textexpander.com/blog/how-to-use-textexpander-for-autocorrection\">How To Use TextExpander for Autocorrection</a></li><li><a href=\"https://textexpander.com/blog/using-snippets-for-your-personal-life\">Using Snippets for Your Personal Life</a></li></ul>\n",
            "content_text": "One of the annual highlights at TextExpander is reading your responses to your end of year summary emails. For TextExpander newbies, each year we send out a summary email containing the stats on how much time you\u2019ve saved by using TextExpander. Data from the number and size of the snippets you\u2019ve expanded is used to calculate roughly how many hours, and often days, you\u2019ve saved. There\u2019s more information on\u00a0how TextExpander works out your time savings here, if you\u2019re curious!\n\n\n\nOur end of year summary is easily one of our favorite emails to send out to our community and we love your feedback. Today, we wanted to share with you not only the time that TextExpander users have saved but a look at how they\u2019ve put that time to use. Here\u2019s how much time the TextExpander community is saving!\n\n\n\nSo How Much Time Did You Save?\n\n\n\nLast year, members of our community clocked up not just hours, but days saved of laborious typing time. For some, it was a couple days freed from typing\u2026\n\n\n\n\nHere's my annual recommendation for @TextExpander, a text auto-replacement program that I've bought and appreciated for many years.If you have messages, code, and snippets that you type repeatedly, a program like this is extremely helpful. pic.twitter.com/KvKeHkTL0V\u2014 W. Eric Martin (@BoardgameNews) January 20, 2022\n\n\n\n\n\nTrue fact: @TextExpander has an internal log that tells me I save 4 days of typing time in 2021\u2014and 34 days since I started using it over a decade ago. It's the one Mac utility I swear by. https://t.co/6TdiawpLHt\u2014 Drummond Reed (@drummondreed) January 20, 2022\n\n\n\n\n\nEfficiency win \ud83d\udcaa I saved 5 days last year with @TextExpander, and 21 days since I started 4 years ago! \ud83e\udd29 https://t.co/fi47bDZx51\u2014 Laura Jolly (@LauraEJolly) January 20, 2022\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nWhile others saved over a week thanks to their speedy snippets\u2026\n\n\n\n\nQuick productivity hack with quantified benefits. In 2021 I saved 7 days (80 WPM in 8-hour days) using @TextExpander shortcuts instead of typing everything. Over the lifetime of use I have now saved 30 days of typing. That is 96,000 keystrokes I haven't had to use#phdchat pic.twitter.com/4OoeuPZf83\u2014 Prof Mark Hutchinson (@prof_hutchinson) January 20, 2022\n\n\n\n\n\nIn 2021, I saved 8 whole days of my life, thanks to @TextExpander.Truly a must-have.(20% off an annual plan \u2013 https://t.co/0KcqpenDEA) pic.twitter.com/ouSozj3SuK\u2014 Rob Bettis (@robbettis) January 20, 2022\n\n\n\n\n\nI saved 10 days last year with @TextExpander! And 36 days since I started. https://t.co/Pz9yrRSwFe\u2014 Don Schaffner \ud83e\udda0 (@bugcounter) January 20, 2022\n\n\n\n\nAnd then some users even clocked in with multiple weeks saved in just one year.\n\n\n\n\nI saved 33 days last year with @TextExpander! And 91 days since I started. https://t.co/vuTJvIWk4J\u2014 \ud83c\udff4\udb40\udc67\udb40\udc62\udb40\udc77\udb40\udc6c\udb40\udc73\udb40\udc7f Stuart \ud83c\udff4\udb40\udc67\udb40\udc62\udb40\udc77\udb40\udc6c\udb40\udc73\udb40\udc7f (@welsh_stu) January 20, 2022\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nHow Did You Spend That Time?\n\n\n\nSome of you even let us know how you put your saved time to good use!\n\n\n\n\nI saved 2 days last year with @TextExpander!  https://t.co/w8Lak1mLBw\u2014 Dr Alison Hardy (@hardy_alison) January 20, 2022\n\n\n\n\n\nI\u2019ve been a @TextExpander user for a few years so this figure is cumulative, but WOW.  This equates to 15.5 work-weeks I\u2019ve saved.Maybe I should take another #epictrip @thesiswhisperer?I\u2019ve earned it. \ud83c\udf66 \ud83c\udf66 \ud83c\udf66 pic.twitter.com/a4TZZRJOcN\u2014 Dr. JD (@jasondowns) January 21, 2022\n\n\n\n\n\n.@TextExpander saved me 9 days of typing just last year. That's a lot of ice cream to eat @jasondowns! pic.twitter.com/Z5b1F1ADaP\u2014 Prof Inger Mewburn (@thesiswhisperer) January 20, 2022\n\n\n\n\nAnd some of you shared the benefits you experienced, too:\n\n\n\n\nAccording to @TextExpander, TextExpander has saved me 6 hours in 2021.I actually think it's much more than that in terms of \"mental energy saved\"! pic.twitter.com/VzFynUe2Wb\u2014 Christoph Janz (@chrija) January 21, 2022\n\n\n\n\nAnd some advice on how to boost your numbers:\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nWhat the TextExpander Team Did With Their Saved Time\n\n\n\nWe asked some of the team what they did with all the time they saved using TextExpander this year. Here\u2019s what they said:\n\n\n\nI used that time to write!My family bought a house, and I spent every saved hour (and then some!) trying to bring it from 1982 to 2022.I used my saved hours to build my spiritual health this past year.I spent my time journaling and meditating, both total gamechangers!\n\n\n\nFind Out How Much Time You\u2019ve Saved\n\n\n\nAlongside our emails, you can find out your own TextExpander time savings whenever you\u2019d like to within the app. Simply open the app, select your username, then select \u201cStatistics\u201d to be taken to your stats page.\n\n\n\nHow much time did you save this year? Let us know. If you want to boost your stats but don\u2019t know where to start, try these posts:\n\n\n\nTextExpander Public Groups 101How To Use TextExpander for AutocorrectionUsing Snippets for Your Personal Life",
